metadata.name: /imagine
metadata.description:
Just imagine what artificial intelligence can bring to the art world.
The history of contemporary art is a history of constant debate about what art is.
Artists, critics, art dealers, ordinary people all have their own opinion about real art. And everyone is trying to express their opinion about the art of artificial intelligence.
Is it just a tool or can it be considered a separate art direction?
In the near future we will witness the rapid development of this direction and it cannot be ignored.

Just imagine...
